# IRC codes

## Usage:

### Text format:
```python
bold(text)
italic(text)
strikethrough(text)
underline(text)
underline2(text)
reverse(text)
text + reset()
```

### Text colors:
```python
colored(text, text_color, background_color)
```

Examples:
```python
colored(text, 'blue')
colored(text, 'light green', 'grey')
```

Supported colors:

| Index | Color       | RGB           |
|-------|-------------|---------------|
| 0     | White       | (255,255,255) |
| 1     | Black       | (0,0,0)       |
| 2     | Blue        | (0,0,127)     |
| 3     | Green       | (0,147,0)     |
| 4     | Light Red   | (255,0,0)     |
| 5     | Brown       | (127,0,0)     |
| 6     | Purple      | (156,0,156)   |
| 7     | Orange      | (252,127,0)   |
| 8     | Yellow      | (255,255,0)   |
| 9     | Light Green | (0,252,0)     |
| 10    | Cyan        | (0,147,147)   |
| 11    | Light Cyan  | (0,255,255)   |
| 12    | Light Blue  | (0,0,252)     |
| 13    | Pink        | (255,0,255)   |
| 14    | Grey        | (127,127,127) |
| 15    | Light Grey  | (210,210,210) |

